WEBVTT

01:35.880 --> 01:41.310
[Pursuit of Jade]

01:41.420 --> 01:43.940
[Episode 5]

01:44.590 --> 01:47.810
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

01:52.509 --> 01:53.509
I won't need this.

01:53.560 --> 01:55.560
He's injured so badly. We won't need this.

01:55.560 --> 01:57.200
You'll need it sooner or later.

01:57.200 --> 01:59.150
Come on, go back to the bridal chamber.

01:59.150 --> 01:59.870
Go on now.

02:10.430 --> 02:11.080
Wait.

02:14.520 --> 02:15.400
I'm sorry.

02:22.630 --> 02:23.560
I'm so used to living alone

02:23.560 --> 02:26.290
that I keep forgetting
there's a man in the house.

02:29.960 --> 02:30.680
Come in.

02:43.190 --> 02:44.050
Let me help you.

02:44.300 --> 02:44.930
No need.

02:47.110 --> 02:48.150
I can do it myself.

02:48.170 --> 02:49.500
What do you mean you can?

02:49.900 --> 02:51.430
You really are impossible.

02:51.430 --> 02:53.790
Is it really that hard to ask someone
to help you apply the medicine?

02:53.790 --> 02:55.800
Your wounds keep flaring up.

02:56.560 --> 02:58.000
Think of how much silver
it'll cost to treat them all,

02:58.000 --> 02:59.930
and how much you'll have to suffer.

03:02.360 --> 03:04.560
Men and women aren't supposed to
get intimate.

03:04.560 --> 03:06.620
What nonsense are you talking about?

03:06.840 --> 03:10.440
The day Song Yan came looking for trouble,
didn't we already k...

03:14.190 --> 03:15.520
Didn't we already kiss?

03:17.710 --> 03:20.150
That's not the kind of intimacy I meant.

03:23.000 --> 03:25.400
Then when I carried you back
from the snow that day—

03:25.400 --> 03:27.200
that counts as intimacy, right?

03:29.980 --> 03:30.630
Yeah, that counts.

03:30.630 --> 03:36.100
[Happiness]

03:31.350 --> 03:32.550
Then that settles it.

03:38.190 --> 03:39.030
Don't worry.

03:39.680 --> 03:41.430
I don't have any improper intentions
toward you.

03:41.430 --> 03:42.630
With all your injuries,

03:41.470 --> 03:43.660
[Happiness]

03:43.079 --> 03:45.540
even if I had such thoughts,
it'd be useless.

03:52.190 --> 03:53.360
Fan Changyu.

03:53.760 --> 03:56.020
Listen to the nonsense you're spouting.

04:00.970 --> 04:03.560
With this kind of medicine,
you don't need to...

04:03.560 --> 04:05.360
You don't need to apply too much.

04:06.400 --> 04:07.200
Is it too much?

04:08.910 --> 04:11.120
But I saw Mr. Zhao use this much.

04:15.360 --> 04:16.430
You changed the medicine?

04:16.430 --> 04:17.690
How come I didn't know?

04:18.390 --> 04:19.240
It's fine.

04:19.950 --> 04:21.410
Just help me bandage it up.

04:30.110 --> 04:31.180
These wounds—

04:31.960 --> 04:34.159
are they all from your escort missions?

04:35.630 --> 04:38.760
I didn't even notice
when I changed your clothes before.

04:39.030 --> 04:39.870
It's nothing.

04:41.190 --> 04:45.790
I didn't want you to come exactly because
I was worried my injuries would scare you.

04:48.040 --> 04:48.870
Bear with it.

04:48.870 --> 04:50.730
I'll have it bandaged in a second.

05:15.040 --> 05:17.770
Others rely on their skills
to escort valuables,

05:18.160 --> 05:20.240
but you rely on sheer luck.

05:24.870 --> 05:26.870
Don't take such risks in the future.

05:27.070 --> 05:28.000
If it comes to it,

05:28.920 --> 05:30.120
I'll just work harder

05:31.380 --> 05:34.240
and slaughter a couple more pigs
to provide for you.

05:53.870 --> 05:56.400
I'll go down
and sleep with Changning in a bit.

05:56.770 --> 05:57.600
No need.

05:58.040 --> 05:58.830
In a bit,

06:00.120 --> 06:02.450
I'll go sleep in the main room downstairs.

06:03.630 --> 06:04.490
That works too.

06:06.070 --> 06:07.480
I'll fetch you a basin of water.

06:07.480 --> 06:09.010
You can wipe yourself down.

06:13.710 --> 06:15.300
I'll take the wedding robes down for you.

06:14.790 --> 06:15.740
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

06:18.660 --> 06:19.580
[Intimacy Instruction Drawings]

06:37.310 --> 06:39.510
Why are you hiding something like this?

06:42.310 --> 06:43.120
That's not mine...

06:43.120 --> 06:45.600
I thought you were
resting and recovering properly!

06:45.600 --> 06:47.220
I never would have guessed.

06:49.159 --> 06:50.870
I won't hold it against you this time.

06:50.870 --> 06:52.360
I'll throw this filthy thing away for you.

06:52.360 --> 06:53.560
No more reading this!

07:01.040 --> 07:02.070
So embarrassing.

07:09.040 --> 07:09.870
What is it?

07:11.890 --> 07:13.120
Come back, come back.

07:13.830 --> 07:15.770
Careful, don't get caught.

07:22.510 --> 07:23.800
She's coming down.

07:57.040 --> 07:57.680
Look.

07:58.100 --> 07:59.270
Was I right or not?

07:59.420 --> 08:02.750
They're sleeping in separate rooms
on their wedding night.

08:02.800 --> 08:05.390
Their marriage must be fake.

08:06.050 --> 08:06.960
Darling,

08:07.160 --> 08:08.630
you really are amazing.

08:08.870 --> 08:10.270
That wretched girl

08:10.390 --> 08:12.510
just wants to deceive the officials

08:12.510 --> 08:14.440
and keep this house all to herself.

08:14.690 --> 08:15.980
Look more closely.

08:16.750 --> 08:18.600
I am looking closely.

08:20.170 --> 08:22.000
I told you to look closely inside!

08:22.000 --> 08:23.530
Who told you to look at this?

08:29.070 --> 08:30.510
Go over there and look.

08:42.980 --> 08:44.880
Darling, this can't be right.

08:45.120 --> 08:47.200
She fetched a basin of water
and went back to the room.

08:47.200 --> 08:48.750
It doesn't look like
they're sleeping in separate rooms.

08:48.750 --> 08:50.890
Don't panic. Watch a bit longer.

08:51.510 --> 08:52.310
What's wrong?

08:56.370 --> 08:59.170
My uncle and aunt are eavesdropping
in the corner.

08:59.600 --> 09:01.130
They might already suspect

09:01.320 --> 09:03.650
that you marrying into our family
is fake.

09:10.670 --> 09:11.930
Come look over here.

09:18.070 --> 09:20.580
Can I stay here for now

09:21.150 --> 09:22.960
and sneak up later?

09:23.930 --> 09:25.330
Just sleep here tonight.

09:28.090 --> 09:29.410
If you leave,

09:29.910 --> 09:31.710
outsiders will get suspicious.

09:32.320 --> 09:33.610
Go close the window.

09:34.960 --> 09:35.560
Okay.

09:43.960 --> 09:45.390
What's this supposed to mean?

09:45.390 --> 09:46.990
They even closed the window.

09:47.270 --> 09:48.600
That's impossible.

09:48.910 --> 09:50.450
In such a short time,

09:51.030 --> 09:52.790
how could that wretched girl have found

09:52.790 --> 09:54.620
a matrilocal husband willing to
deal with her?

09:54.620 --> 09:55.880
Something must be off.

10:04.870 --> 10:06.000
Give me the candles.

10:13.550 --> 10:14.350
Sit over here.

10:31.840 --> 10:32.630
Turn around.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.510
Come closer.

10:51.630 --> 10:53.480
A-Are they about to
consummate the marriage?

10:53.480 --> 10:55.250
Right here in the main room...

10:55.440 --> 10:57.040
Consummating the marriage?

11:01.060 --> 11:04.070
Your clothes are soaked with sweat.

11:04.300 --> 11:05.500
Why don't you change?

11:13.870 --> 11:15.180
Take off my clothes.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.170
Help me lie down.

12:28.600 --> 12:29.460
Don't move.

12:33.960 --> 12:34.920
Darling, look.

12:34.940 --> 12:36.670
It's exactly like in that book.

12:37.490 --> 12:38.880
Stop reading it!

12:40.670 --> 12:42.660
That wretched girl has no shame.

13:18.380 --> 13:19.720
Blow out the candles.

13:26.080 --> 13:27.870
Darling, even the lights are out.

13:27.870 --> 13:28.670
Show's over.

13:29.030 --> 13:29.910
Let's go.

13:30.540 --> 13:31.180
Wait.

13:32.150 --> 13:33.440
I have a feeling that

13:34.120 --> 13:35.780
this is not what it looks like.

13:37.750 --> 13:38.880
Where are you going?

13:39.120 --> 13:40.450
I'll climb back over

13:40.550 --> 13:41.810
and take a closer look.

13:51.030 --> 13:52.270
Darn stray cat!

13:52.440 --> 13:54.440
Sneaking in to steal our meat again.

13:55.320 --> 13:56.300
It's not a cat?

13:56.600 --> 13:57.670
Who's out there?

14:04.750 --> 14:06.340
As expected from a beast.

14:06.360 --> 14:07.550
Shameless thing.

14:07.570 --> 14:09.100
Stealing meat in the middle of the night.

14:09.100 --> 14:10.360
If I catch you next time,

14:10.360 --> 14:11.690
I won't let you off easy!

14:16.190 --> 14:19.920
Could that wretched girl
really have consummated their marriage?

14:20.960 --> 14:22.790
Then... Then let's hurry
and get out of here.

14:22.790 --> 14:25.200
Or we'll end up kicking the bucket
right here.

14:25.200 --> 14:26.200
Hurry up. Come on.

14:57.910 --> 14:58.640
Thanks a lot.

15:24.480 --> 15:26.340
[Fan's Butcher Shop]

15:40.120 --> 15:41.080
Just this piece, right?

15:41.080 --> 15:42.080
Yeah, this piece.

15:42.480 --> 15:43.000
Look,

15:43.100 --> 15:44.280
full weight.

15:44.300 --> 15:45.000
Come again.

15:45.000 --> 15:45.650
Sure.

15:45.690 --> 15:46.720
Want some braised pork?

15:46.720 --> 15:47.160
Yeah, this.

15:47.160 --> 15:47.870
Pig ears.

15:49.230 --> 15:50.000
One catty.

15:50.820 --> 15:51.350
Here.

15:52.240 --> 15:53.000
Thanks.

15:53.120 --> 15:54.300
Perfect mix of fat and lean, right?

15:54.300 --> 15:55.230
Yeah, it's good.

15:57.870 --> 15:58.870
Thank you, Boss.

16:09.220 --> 16:10.480
Boss, I want some meat.

16:12.950 --> 16:13.640
Coming.

16:15.630 --> 16:16.760
How about 2 catties?

16:16.780 --> 16:17.780
Sure, that works.

16:17.840 --> 16:20.360
[Pork Head Meat] [Spices]

16:22.250 --> 16:23.360
Not bad.

16:23.600 --> 16:24.600
Sold out already.

16:24.670 --> 16:25.670
Mrs. Yin.

16:26.150 --> 16:26.840
Changyu,

16:27.400 --> 16:29.400
why open up right after the wedding?

16:29.440 --> 16:30.850
Why not rest more at home?

16:31.170 --> 16:32.810
I want to earn more money

16:32.840 --> 16:35.050
to get my parents' pig shed
running again soon,

16:35.050 --> 16:36.250
so I have to work hard.

16:37.520 --> 16:40.400
True, another mouth to feed at home.

16:40.550 --> 16:41.880
You do need to work hard.

16:44.080 --> 16:45.600
That matrilocal husband of yours—

16:45.600 --> 16:47.510
how was his performance last night?

16:47.510 --> 16:49.120
Pretty good. He eats well and sleeps well,

16:49.120 --> 16:49.960
and his injuries are healing well.

16:49.960 --> 16:51.360
Who asked about that?

16:51.510 --> 16:54.120
Having a baby is a big deal.

16:54.670 --> 16:57.330
Your matrilocal husband
looks tall and strong.

16:57.750 --> 16:59.410
He should be good at it, right?

16:59.690 --> 17:01.220
What are you talking about?

17:01.270 --> 17:02.350
Look at you.

17:02.390 --> 17:03.790
I don't even understand.

17:04.240 --> 17:06.700
-Stop pretending.
-Keep moving. Follow up!

17:18.800 --> 17:20.329
What's going on now?

17:21.069 --> 17:23.869
They're catching refugees
from Chongzhou again.

17:28.339 --> 17:29.880
Mrs. Yin, watch the shop for me.

17:29.880 --> 17:31.010
I'll be right back.

17:32.640 --> 17:33.770
Where are you going?

17:35.990 --> 17:39.760
[Government]

17:42.070 --> 17:42.960
It's all done.

17:43.070 --> 17:44.200
Put it away quickly.

17:45.440 --> 17:46.570
Thank you, Mr. Wang.

17:47.740 --> 17:48.800
Come here, please.

17:53.590 --> 17:54.240
What is it?

17:56.000 --> 17:57.390
This is for your trouble.

17:57.390 --> 17:58.740
No need for money.

17:59.510 --> 18:01.030
You two are already married.

18:01.030 --> 18:02.560
It's perfectly legal.

18:03.550 --> 18:05.320
Don't treat me like a stranger.

18:08.200 --> 18:09.530
Thank you then, Mr. Wang.

18:09.530 --> 18:10.330
It's nothing.

18:10.480 --> 18:10.960
Alright.

18:10.960 --> 18:12.160
It's cold. Go on home.

18:18.350 --> 18:20.810
[Luo's Pawnshop]

18:28.060 --> 18:29.120
[One silver hairpin pawned for
2 taels of pure silver]

18:28.160 --> 18:29.270
It's sold. Sold already.

18:29.270 --> 18:30.160
Sold?

18:31.160 --> 18:32.540
How could you sell it?

18:33.030 --> 18:34.430
It was a redeemable pawn.

18:34.480 --> 18:36.280
Look closely at the pawn ticket.

18:36.830 --> 18:38.510
It was indeed a redeemable pawn,

18:38.510 --> 18:40.680
but there's a stipulation:

18:40.820 --> 18:45.230
[Luo's Pawnshop]

18:41.110 --> 18:43.680
if unredeemed within 10 days,
it becomes a forfeitable pawn.

18:43.680 --> 18:44.200
Look,

18:44.240 --> 18:46.780
this is the contract you signed yourself.

18:47.440 --> 18:49.770
That line is so tiny—
who could even see it?

18:50.160 --> 18:53.200
And even if I did see it,
I wouldn't be able to read it anyway.

18:53.200 --> 18:53.960
Mrs. Fan,

18:54.400 --> 18:55.920
you can't expect me to teach you
how to read

18:55.920 --> 18:57.850
when you come to pawn goods, right?

18:58.830 --> 18:59.830
You scammed me!

19:01.000 --> 19:03.460
I did everything according to
the contract.

19:04.070 --> 19:05.400
I really don't understand.

19:05.400 --> 19:06.570
Just a crude silver hairpin—

19:06.570 --> 19:07.880
that gentleman wanted it,

19:07.880 --> 19:08.980
and now you want to redeem it.

19:08.980 --> 19:10.070
It's not like it's anything
rare or valuable.

19:10.070 --> 19:11.000
What gentleman?

19:11.030 --> 19:11.890
Where did he go?

19:12.680 --> 19:14.240
Well, the customer's information...

19:14.240 --> 19:14.880
Speak!

19:21.070 --> 19:22.470
That was the only memento

19:23.000 --> 19:24.530
my parents left me.

19:27.510 --> 19:29.110
It was just a young man.

19:29.130 --> 19:30.900
I really don't know who he is.

19:31.510 --> 19:33.040
How much did you sell it for?

19:34.240 --> 19:35.160
Just 20 taels.

19:36.960 --> 19:38.440
How could you sell it

19:38.440 --> 19:40.770
just because someone offered more money?

19:41.640 --> 19:43.440
We have the pawn ticket as proof.

19:43.440 --> 19:46.020
Even if you sue me
at the county government office,

19:46.020 --> 19:47.550
I'm not afraid of you, okay?

19:55.980 --> 19:56.250
[Luo's Pawnshop]

20:18.270 --> 20:20.560
Changyu? Why are you here?

20:22.750 --> 20:24.490
What's wrong with her today?

20:38.770 --> 20:39.390
Changyu.

20:54.780 --> 20:55.160
Dad.

20:55.160 --> 20:58.790
The candy I hid for so long
was eaten by ants.

20:59.880 --> 21:01.320
There, there. Don't cry.

21:01.510 --> 21:03.710
Didn't I come up with a solution for you?

21:07.910 --> 21:09.190
Look at this.

21:10.590 --> 21:12.390
Now the ants can't eat it, right?

21:12.720 --> 21:14.310
You are amazing, Dad.

21:14.400 --> 21:15.160
Can you

21:15.160 --> 21:17.710
hide these candies in there for me?

21:19.470 --> 21:20.690
You little rascal.

21:20.920 --> 21:22.990
I knew you were hiding more candy.

21:23.240 --> 21:24.920
Don't tell your mother.

21:24.940 --> 21:26.720
Or she'll scold both of us.

21:26.720 --> 21:28.020
Got it, Dad.

21:30.110 --> 21:31.960
Go pick a blade of grass for me.

21:35.750 --> 21:36.680
Here, Dad.

21:40.070 --> 21:41.200
This way,

21:42.030 --> 21:43.440
you won't lose it, right?

21:43.750 --> 21:45.180
You're the best, Dad.

21:45.550 --> 21:46.330
You, oh you.

21:49.680 --> 21:50.350
Remember:

21:50.790 --> 21:52.550
hardships come, hardships go.

21:53.160 --> 21:54.160
Tears may fall,

21:54.310 --> 21:56.000
but you must keep moving forward.

21:56.000 --> 21:58.310
Even if the sky falls, there's always
someone taller to hold it up.

21:58.310 --> 22:00.930
We must always eat well and sleep well.

22:00.960 --> 22:02.160
Got it, Dad.

22:02.790 --> 22:03.560
Good girl.

22:32.310 --> 22:33.720
Thank you.

22:34.020 --> 22:35.540
Many thanks.

22:35.720 --> 22:36.830
See you another day.

22:36.830 --> 22:37.680
See you.

22:37.680 --> 22:38.550
I'm off.

22:40.270 --> 22:41.640
Take care.

22:41.680 --> 22:43.000
Ms. Song.

22:43.880 --> 22:44.960
Ms. Song.

22:45.030 --> 22:47.680
You're moving to a big mansion
in the city, right?

22:47.680 --> 22:49.610
How blessed you are.

22:49.680 --> 22:51.550
The County Magistrate
thinks highly of him,

22:51.550 --> 22:53.810
and our Yan has lived up to expectations.

22:53.830 --> 22:55.070
I'm thinking next year,

22:55.070 --> 22:56.310
he'll take first place in
all 3 imperial exams

22:56.310 --> 22:58.480
and bring glory to our town.

22:58.500 --> 23:00.160
He'll surely pass with flying colors.

23:00.160 --> 23:02.400
I'll take your good word for it, Sis.

23:05.270 --> 23:06.310
Sis,

23:06.550 --> 23:10.000
now that your Song Yan is about to become

23:10.000 --> 23:12.480
the County Magistrate's son-in-law,

23:13.510 --> 23:17.160
as for your promise of getting
my eldest grandson out of corvée labor

23:17.160 --> 23:19.830
and finding him a job
as a police runner back home—

23:19.830 --> 23:21.480
when will that happen?

23:24.350 --> 23:27.780
I've spread the word to the whole village

23:27.880 --> 23:30.240
that Fan Changyu is a jinx for you.

23:30.680 --> 23:31.480
Nonsense.

23:31.790 --> 23:34.050
When did I ever ask you
to spread any word?

23:34.930 --> 23:36.810
No, no. Nothing.

23:36.840 --> 23:38.100
I didn't say anything.

23:38.550 --> 23:39.810
Don't worry.

23:40.270 --> 23:41.640
When there's a chance,

23:41.680 --> 23:44.210
I'll have Yan speak to
the County Magistrate.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.700
Understood. Understood.

23:46.510 --> 23:48.170
Fan Changyu, hold on, please.

23:49.720 --> 23:50.960
Stop right there!

23:52.750 --> 23:54.710
Hardships come, hardships go.

23:55.160 --> 23:58.820
Even if the sky falls, there's always
someone taller to hold it up.

24:04.590 --> 24:08.050
We've been neighbors for years,
and we may not meet ever again.

24:08.560 --> 24:10.560
This is a token of our appreciation.

24:10.590 --> 24:11.790
Please accept it.

24:12.240 --> 24:15.070
And please, return
the betrothal letter to us.

24:16.110 --> 24:17.000
Exactly.

24:17.240 --> 24:19.270
Now that you've taken a matrilocal husband
and gotten married,

24:19.270 --> 24:21.270
why keep their betrothal letter?

24:25.720 --> 24:26.720
That's all?

24:28.020 --> 24:30.360
How much do we owe you exactly?

24:30.720 --> 24:33.070
Besides, when did that even happen?

24:33.100 --> 24:34.240
And who saw it?

24:35.030 --> 24:35.790
Exactly.

24:35.980 --> 24:38.040
Without proof, who would believe it?

24:38.200 --> 24:40.440
If the Song family really
borrowed money from you,

24:40.440 --> 24:42.880
you would have asked for it back
the next year.

24:42.880 --> 24:45.480
Who would give charity for over a decade

24:45.480 --> 24:47.350
without expecting anything in return?
Right?

24:47.350 --> 24:50.080
That would make them a living saint,
wouldn't it?

24:57.440 --> 24:58.440
Fine, never mind.

24:59.920 --> 25:01.600
I'll give you all this money.

25:01.790 --> 25:02.680
This must be enough, right?

25:02.680 --> 25:04.610
Give us back the betrothal letter.

25:10.650 --> 25:12.130
Everyone, look!

25:12.510 --> 25:14.440
Even this much money isn't enough.

25:14.550 --> 25:16.160
You, Fan Changyu,

25:16.160 --> 25:17.830
are truly insatiable!

25:18.480 --> 25:20.140
You've been blinded by greed!

25:20.200 --> 25:21.680
What kind of person is she?

25:23.830 --> 25:25.950
Move. Move aside.

25:26.030 --> 25:27.680
Bad people are bullying Changyu,

25:27.680 --> 25:29.680
and Zheng is here to back her up.

25:35.920 --> 25:36.680
Who is this?

25:37.100 --> 25:38.710
This is Changyu's husband.

25:38.790 --> 25:39.790
Him?

25:40.070 --> 25:41.300
And he's a cripple.

25:44.110 --> 25:45.500
Your wounds haven't healed.

25:45.500 --> 25:46.540
It's hard for you to move around.

25:46.540 --> 25:48.540
Why are you messing around with her?

25:48.660 --> 25:49.420
It's fine.

25:52.480 --> 25:54.340
Even if my wounds haven't healed,

25:54.830 --> 25:57.430
it doesn't stop me from
coming to take you home.

26:00.480 --> 26:04.200
What does the Fan family's business have
to do with a matrilocal husband like you?

26:04.200 --> 26:05.660
My surname is also Fan now.

26:06.720 --> 26:07.880
You want an IOU?

26:08.320 --> 26:08.950
Fine.

26:09.830 --> 26:12.690
Clear the debts you Song family
owes the Fan family,

26:12.830 --> 26:14.000
then you can move.

26:15.590 --> 26:17.830
One coffin—6 taels and 20 mace.

26:18.330 --> 26:20.730
Twelve chi of fine cloth—
1 tael and 10 mace.

26:21.510 --> 26:23.840
Thirty baskets of eggs—
1 tael and 50 mace.

26:25.160 --> 26:27.920
Three years of tuition—
9 taels and 60 mace.

26:29.680 --> 26:31.550
Song Yan, that poor scholar,

26:31.920 --> 26:33.700
only managed to study thanks to

26:33.730 --> 26:35.460
the Fan family supporting him.

26:35.480 --> 26:36.480
Who would have thought that

26:36.480 --> 26:39.110
as soon as Song Yan became
a provincial candidate,

26:39.110 --> 26:41.380
while Fan Erniu and his wife
were barely cold in their graves,

26:41.380 --> 26:43.980
he forced Changyu to
break off the engagement?

26:44.110 --> 26:45.590
Song's mother's living expenses

26:45.590 --> 26:47.440
were also paid for
entirely by Changyu's family.

26:47.440 --> 26:48.240
How shameless.

26:48.240 --> 26:49.110
Exactly.

26:53.640 --> 26:55.970
Mr. Zhao, what exactly were the expenses?

26:56.000 --> 26:58.890
They paid 3 years of tuition
for that ingrate.

26:59.110 --> 27:01.720
One year alone costs 3 taels and 20 mace.

27:02.120 --> 27:04.780
Do the math—how much would that be
after 3 years?

27:05.000 --> 27:06.270
Nine taels and 60 mace.

27:06.750 --> 27:07.880
That's quite a lot.

27:07.900 --> 27:10.110
And the pork they begged for
during festivals—

27:10.110 --> 27:12.000
at least 20 pieces.

27:12.160 --> 27:14.110
That must add up to
over 2 taels of silver.

27:14.110 --> 27:16.710
And when Song Yan got sick
the year before last,

27:16.720 --> 27:18.950
the medicine alone cost over a tael.

27:19.030 --> 27:20.560
Fan Erniu paid for that too.

27:20.690 --> 27:21.890
He didn't even dare tell his wife

27:21.890 --> 27:23.350
or Changyu.

27:23.350 --> 27:24.880
The more we talk about it,
the madder I get.

27:24.880 --> 27:26.610
Even the women's items like...

27:32.200 --> 27:34.930
And 4 packs of bamboo baskets,
30 bundles of wood,

27:34.960 --> 27:35.750
5 buckets of lamp oil,

27:35.750 --> 27:36.750
3 copper basins,

27:37.530 --> 27:38.620
one bamboo mat,

27:38.640 --> 27:39.660
and...

27:40.640 --> 27:41.360
Changning, come back.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.820
Don't fall into the ditch.

27:44.640 --> 27:47.200
And 4 bundles of menstrual cloths.

27:48.790 --> 27:49.640
Menstrual cloths?

27:49.640 --> 27:52.720
-They even borrowed the menstrual cloths?
-And last year on the Dragon Boat Festival,

27:52.720 --> 27:54.270
Mrs. Song came to visit

27:54.400 --> 27:57.590
and took the chance to steal
a braised pig's tail.

27:59.370 --> 28:00.850
So, all things considered,

28:00.850 --> 28:01.900
the Fan family

28:01.920 --> 28:04.580
basically provided for
the Song mother and son.

28:05.010 --> 28:07.550
Granny Kang, you were speaking up
for the Song family just now—

28:07.550 --> 28:09.750
how much of the benefits did you pocket?

28:09.920 --> 28:11.230
Don't talk nonsense.

28:11.270 --> 28:12.950
I've never gotten anything out of it.

28:12.950 --> 28:14.510
I'm just like everyone else.

28:14.510 --> 28:16.190
I was just passing by.

28:16.350 --> 28:19.060
Seriously, I've never gotten anything.

28:19.270 --> 28:20.850
I was just passing by.

28:21.200 --> 28:22.590
You're a grown man,

28:22.610 --> 28:25.270
talking about women's filthy things
all the time—

28:25.270 --> 28:27.110
what a disgrace to decency!

28:28.090 --> 28:31.000
Menstruation is the foundation
of humanity and motherhood.

28:31.000 --> 28:32.790
Why can't it be spoken of?

28:32.950 --> 28:35.030
You say it can't be spoken of,

28:35.200 --> 28:36.860
but you sure ask for things often.

28:36.860 --> 28:39.020
Exactly, asking for a whole bundle
at once.

28:39.020 --> 28:40.590
If your period lasts half a month,

28:40.590 --> 28:42.480
you'd better see a doctor soon.

28:42.480 --> 28:44.390
-Go see a doctor.
-Go see a doctor.

28:44.720 --> 28:45.980
None of your business!

28:46.400 --> 28:47.800
What are you laughing at?

28:48.590 --> 28:50.000
None of your business!

28:50.270 --> 28:51.270
What's so funny?

28:51.350 --> 28:52.640
It's none of your business!

28:52.640 --> 28:54.900
Ladies, please don't use hurtful words.

28:56.350 --> 28:58.070
You underestimate Mr. and Mrs. Fan's

28:58.070 --> 28:59.440
sincere care for me.

29:00.070 --> 29:01.110
They've passed away,

29:01.110 --> 29:02.970
so there should be no more gossip.

29:03.310 --> 29:03.880
Changyu.

29:05.190 --> 29:07.450
Although you always speak harshly to me,

29:07.880 --> 29:08.960
I don't blame you.

29:10.640 --> 29:12.830
I know your hasty marriage this time

29:13.440 --> 29:14.970
has something to do with me.

29:16.680 --> 29:18.010
Even though from now on,

29:18.110 --> 29:19.680
we'll go our separate ways,

29:20.680 --> 29:22.880
if you encounter trouble in the future,

29:23.000 --> 29:25.600
just send someone to my mansion
and let me know.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.310
I will always be your Brother Song Yan.

29:27.310 --> 29:28.160
Bah!

29:28.830 --> 29:30.890
Don't disgust me with that nonsense.

29:31.030 --> 29:32.510
If not for my sake,

29:33.070 --> 29:36.130
would my parents have treated
someone like you so well?

29:36.240 --> 29:38.240
I blame myself for
being blind and foolish.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.270
I was truly blind,

29:40.210 --> 29:42.710
falling for a literate ingrate like you.

29:42.920 --> 29:43.320
You...

29:43.590 --> 29:45.400
You, pay up!

29:46.230 --> 29:47.070
-That's right!
-Pay her!

29:47.070 --> 29:48.120
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

29:48.120 --> 29:48.950
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

29:48.950 --> 29:50.160
-Pay her!
-Pay her!

29:50.720 --> 29:51.510
Fine.

29:52.590 --> 29:55.250
A gentleman never speaks ill of
a former friend.

29:55.750 --> 29:56.990
I will pay you back.

29:59.030 --> 30:00.110
Removing the fraction,

30:00.110 --> 30:01.370
it's 30 taels in total.

30:01.400 --> 30:04.060
If you don't believe me,
calculate it yourself.

30:06.890 --> 30:07.530
Mother,

30:08.290 --> 30:09.200
pay her.

30:12.720 --> 30:14.580
But we don't have that much money.

30:17.200 --> 30:18.550
If you don't have enough money,

30:18.550 --> 30:19.680
you can write an IOU.

30:21.310 --> 30:22.910
There's no ink or brush here.

30:23.350 --> 30:25.020
I'll write one and send it to you
once I move to the city.

30:25.020 --> 30:26.260
Why do you need ink?

30:26.790 --> 30:28.270
Bite your finger open,

30:28.680 --> 30:30.680
and press your fingerprint. That will do.

30:30.680 --> 30:31.880
Right. Press your fingerprint.

30:31.880 --> 30:33.700
Just press your fingerprint.

30:33.830 --> 30:34.240
Hurry up.

30:34.240 --> 30:35.380
Absolutely not!

30:35.440 --> 30:36.640
Don't listen to them.

30:37.550 --> 30:38.010
This...

30:38.690 --> 30:39.950
-Don't do that!
-Wait!

30:56.140 --> 30:57.790
It's only a few dozen taels.

30:56.430 --> 30:59.470
[Daughter of Magistrate Cui]

30:57.830 --> 30:59.160
I'll pay it back for him.

31:03.110 --> 31:04.310
Miss Cui Qianjin.

31:04.310 --> 31:07.390
How could we trouble you
to step into such a lowly place?

31:08.550 --> 31:10.960
Brother Song is my father's student.

31:11.270 --> 31:12.270
It's only right

31:12.480 --> 31:13.540
that I help him out.

31:15.110 --> 31:16.960
How can a dignified imperial scholar

31:16.960 --> 31:18.850
be schemed against and sullied

31:18.920 --> 31:20.720
by some people reeking of money?

31:33.200 --> 31:35.640
Some are born with noble lives.

31:36.270 --> 31:36.960
Like me.

31:37.830 --> 31:40.030
My father named me Qianjin,

31:40.200 --> 31:42.350
destining me to never lack gold or silver,

31:42.350 --> 31:43.880
and to order others around.

31:44.590 --> 31:47.680
Some are born with cheap lives.

31:48.310 --> 31:49.000
Like you.

31:49.920 --> 31:51.590
Both parents dead since childhood,

31:51.590 --> 31:53.440
with no one to rely on in this life.

31:53.440 --> 31:55.110
No matter how beautiful jade is,

31:55.110 --> 31:57.240
it's not as valuable as gold or silver.

31:57.720 --> 31:58.920
Here's 50 taels.

31:59.510 --> 32:00.570
Go on and pick it up.

32:12.880 --> 32:14.010
Stop it, Changning.

32:14.400 --> 32:16.060
We won't take what's not ours.

32:16.590 --> 32:18.750
The betrothal letter has long been placed
under the stone slab

32:18.750 --> 32:20.210
at your house's doorstep.

32:20.920 --> 32:21.550
Mother...

32:22.790 --> 32:24.920
Things have long been over between us.

32:25.750 --> 32:28.150
Consider the extra money as interest.

32:28.310 --> 32:30.270
After all, your dignity

32:30.750 --> 32:32.150
isn't worth much anyway.

32:32.430 --> 32:34.110
I won't take a penny less than
what I'm owed,

32:34.110 --> 32:35.590
and I won't take a penny
that isn't supposed to be mine.

32:35.590 --> 32:36.270
Besides,

32:37.710 --> 32:39.110
he's not worth anything.

32:41.880 --> 32:43.880
Wait! I haven't finished speaking!

32:43.930 --> 32:44.730
Get back here!

32:44.750 --> 32:45.510
-How rude!
-Yan.

32:45.510 --> 32:47.070
Yan, come and help!

32:47.310 --> 32:47.880
Hurry up!

32:49.830 --> 32:50.720
Whoever goes to help,

32:50.720 --> 32:52.650
the silver on the ground is theirs!

33:06.650 --> 33:08.180
Alright, alright. Come on.

33:10.440 --> 33:11.200
Finally...

33:15.000 --> 33:16.160
Finally found it.

33:18.000 --> 33:18.980
Tear it up.

33:23.970 --> 33:25.900
Changning, go home with Zheng.

33:48.110 --> 33:50.040
He's just a provincial candidate.

33:50.200 --> 33:52.120
In our Great Yin's 1 capital city
and 17 prefectures,

33:52.120 --> 33:53.920
how many provincial candidates
are there each year?

33:53.920 --> 33:55.850
What does a mere Song Yan count for?

33:59.590 --> 34:00.850
You can say such things

34:01.030 --> 34:02.680
in front of me,

34:03.380 --> 34:05.440
but don't say them in front of outsiders.

34:05.440 --> 34:06.640
You'll be laughed at.

34:06.720 --> 34:07.640
Laughed at?

34:09.110 --> 34:10.030
For what?

34:10.630 --> 34:11.989
They'll laugh at you

34:12.070 --> 34:14.469
for not even being a provincial candidate.

34:19.230 --> 34:21.920
I know you're just saying this
to cheer me up.

34:24.020 --> 34:25.320
Why would I try to cheer you up?

34:25.320 --> 34:26.800
Don't mention a provincial candidate—

34:26.800 --> 34:28.199
even an imperial scholar

34:28.590 --> 34:29.880
is nothing special.

34:32.840 --> 34:36.190
Do you really think of yourself
as a high-ranking official or something?

34:36.190 --> 34:36.480
I...

34:36.670 --> 34:38.020
I think you're smart,

34:38.480 --> 34:40.400
and your handwriting is nice, too.

34:40.400 --> 34:43.190
Why don't you go study
and take the imperial exams too?

34:43.190 --> 34:44.630
If you happen to pass
and become a provincial candidate,

34:44.630 --> 34:46.710
you might also land yourself
an official position.

34:46.710 --> 34:48.639
I have no interest in officialdom.

34:51.480 --> 34:53.030
That's a shame.

34:53.239 --> 34:56.230
I was hoping you'd become
a very, very, very high-ranking official—

34:56.230 --> 34:59.760
so you could find some reason
to make life hard for that Song guy.

35:01.890 --> 35:02.440
Okay.

35:07.710 --> 35:08.510
What's wrong?

35:12.710 --> 35:14.110
Actually, I'm not sad

35:15.510 --> 35:16.670
because of Song Yan.

35:18.800 --> 35:21.930
I'm sad because I couldn't get
my mother's hairpin back.

35:33.440 --> 35:36.900
-Actually, that hairpin...
-I've really let my parents down.

35:37.360 --> 35:39.590
I clearly pawned it as a redeemable pawn,

35:39.590 --> 35:41.630
but I happened to run into
a dishonest shopkeeper

35:41.630 --> 35:44.070
who sold it to
some dim-witted young gentleman.

35:44.070 --> 35:45.290
That darn gentleman

35:45.320 --> 35:46.920
actually paid 20 taels of silver for it!

35:46.920 --> 35:48.520
20 taels of silver, you know?

35:48.590 --> 35:50.180
With that much money,

35:50.320 --> 35:52.320
I could have made 3 hairpins for him.

35:53.410 --> 35:55.000
How can there be such a person

35:55.000 --> 35:56.530
who just causes trouble...

36:08.510 --> 36:09.990
Why do you have this?

36:10.320 --> 36:11.380
That gentleman...

36:15.510 --> 36:17.910
So it was you who spent 20 taels
to redeem it?

36:19.880 --> 36:21.240
Sort of.

36:26.140 --> 36:27.080
It's back.

36:32.710 --> 36:33.400
Wait.

36:34.110 --> 36:35.270
So, all in all,

36:36.030 --> 36:38.920
that dishonest shopkeeper
cheated you out of 20 taels?

36:38.920 --> 36:40.650
I have to get that money back...

36:45.590 --> 36:47.070
Actually, that gentleman

36:48.180 --> 36:49.790
is the bookshop owner.

36:50.790 --> 36:52.860
He bought this hairpin for 20 taels.

36:55.480 --> 36:57.030
He appreciates my writings,

36:57.030 --> 37:00.110
so when he sent someone
to deliver my payment,

37:00.400 --> 37:02.260
he rewarded me with this hairpin.

37:02.440 --> 37:04.040
That's quite a coincidence.

37:05.150 --> 37:05.760
Yeah.

37:10.900 --> 37:11.900
Here's the money.

37:17.590 --> 37:18.920
You made that much money

37:19.310 --> 37:20.660
selling essays?

37:20.850 --> 37:22.930
Yes. Mr. Zhao can testify.

37:23.490 --> 37:24.820
Where is that bookshop?

37:25.550 --> 37:27.030
I'll go return the money
to that gentleman.

37:27.030 --> 37:27.630
No need.

37:28.360 --> 37:30.160
That gentleman is very wealthy.

37:30.320 --> 37:31.950
He doesn't care about 20 taels.

37:31.950 --> 37:33.480
I should at least thank him.

37:35.230 --> 37:36.150
Of course.

37:37.230 --> 37:39.700
When my injuries heal,

37:39.960 --> 37:41.420
I'll take you to visit him.

37:42.920 --> 37:43.630
Alright.

37:47.230 --> 37:48.150
Actually,

37:48.710 --> 37:51.570
you don't have to sell essays
to support the family.

37:52.920 --> 37:53.840
I told you,

37:55.190 --> 37:57.250
I can support you by butchering pigs.

38:19.980 --> 38:23.860
[Memorial Tablet of Meng Lihua]
[Memorial Tablet of Fan Erniu]

38:20.920 --> 38:21.670
Mother.

38:22.030 --> 38:23.630
I've retrieved the hairpin.

38:24.590 --> 38:25.360
Before,

38:26.190 --> 38:28.790
I kept worrying
that I'd done something wrong,

38:29.280 --> 38:30.920
worried that you wouldn't approve of
what I did,

38:30.920 --> 38:32.520
worried that you'd be angry.

38:33.510 --> 38:34.710
Now that this hairpin

38:34.840 --> 38:36.370
has found its way back to me,

38:37.960 --> 38:40.360
it must be you watching over us
from beyond.

38:43.110 --> 38:45.440
With that, my heart
can finally be at ease.

39:01.340 --> 39:02.200
Let me help you.

40:12.740 --> 40:17.950
[Luyuan Academy of Hejian]

40:44.760 --> 40:45.440
An.

40:45.800 --> 40:46.480
I've got drumsticks here.

40:46.480 --> 40:47.410
Do you want some?

40:49.030 --> 40:49.630
I...

40:51.400 --> 40:52.730
I don't eat drumsticks.

40:52.750 --> 40:54.000
I've got a big one here.

40:54.000 --> 40:55.030
Look.

40:57.150 --> 40:58.710
This is highly inappropriate.

40:58.710 --> 41:01.240
How can you eat meat
in such a refined academy?

41:01.780 --> 41:04.640
Aren't you worried
the Headmaster will punish you?

41:48.630 --> 41:49.820
You stupid bird.

41:49.880 --> 41:51.940
You get lost every time you come here.

41:57.070 --> 41:58.110
I know, I know.

41:58.110 --> 41:59.910
Wait a moment. Stay here for now.

42:02.360 --> 42:04.440
Today's punishment copying
is considered done.

42:04.440 --> 42:05.360
You may leave.

42:07.190 --> 42:08.480
Thank you, Headmaster.

42:08.480 --> 42:10.400
An, thank the Headmaster.

42:11.670 --> 42:13.470
Thank you, Headmaster Gongsun.

42:20.520 --> 42:22.680
I'm temporarily staying with the Fan family
in Lin'an Town to recover from my injuries.

42:22.400 --> 42:24.460
[I'm temporarily staying with the Fan family
in Lin'an Town to recover from my injuries.]

42:23.480 --> 42:25.320
I've brought my household registration
and travel permit with me

42:24.480 --> 42:26.090
[I've brought my household registration
and travel permit with me for verification.]
[Jiuheng]

42:25.390 --> 42:26.450
for verification.

42:34.230 --> 42:35.770
Xie Jiuheng, you rascal.

42:36.070 --> 42:38.570
I knew you wouldn't die so easily.
